2. play around with a bunch of different colors and patterns to see what you feel most confident in (confidence is key!)

left or right side?🥰
.
.
outfit links will be posted in my bio!! to be fair I think the two styles can be used in both country aesthetics but just my overall take on current fall trends😌

I think I’m always seeing Korean influencers wearing big chunky sweaters with mini skirts or just tighter bottoms and knee high boots for a “cuter” look on insta and different online shops etc.

whereas in the US I’ve seen more of “old money” aesthetics with a mix of preppy and classy (striped sweaters, a-line skirts and overcoats)

I think both can agree tho that the mini skirt + knee high boots combo is IN right now🤩
